repair.repairedDockerfile:
FROM node:16.0.0

# Includes ffprobe
RUN apt-get update && apt-get -y --no-install-recommends install ffmpeg

WORKDIR /app

# make ss commands work
COPY ./package.json .
COPY ./yarn.lock .
RUN yarn
COPY ./bin bin
COPY ./scripts scripts
COPY ./gulpfile.ts .
ENV PATH="/app/bin:${PATH}"

# install api dependencies
COPY ./api/package.json api/
COPY ./api/yarn.lock api/
RUN ss installapi

# install web dependencies
COPY ./web/package.json web/
COPY ./web/yarn.lock web/
RUN ss installweb

# copy the web files over
COPY ./web/tsconfig.json web/
COPY ./web/craco.config.js web/
COPY ./web/.env web/

# copy the api files over
COPY ./api/tsconfig.json api/
COPY ./api/tsconfig.prod.json api/
COPY ./api/jest.config.js api/
COPY ./api/src api/src/

# build the api project
RUN yarn tsc --project api/tsconfig.prod.json

# run the project
CMD [ "yarn", "prod:api" ]
